$lang['There are many tools available online that can help with converting between decimal and hexadecimal numbers. Additionally, most calculators have a built-in function that will allow you to do this conversion very easily. With just a few clicks of the mouse or taps on the keyboard, you’ll be able to change any decimal value into its corresponding hexadecimal equivalent!'] = 'Akwai kayan aikin da yawa da ake samu akan layi waɗanda zasu iya taimakawa tare da juyawa tsakanin lambobi na decimal da hexadecimal. Bugu da ƙari, yawancin ƙididdiga suna da ginanniyar aikin da zai ba ku damar yin wannan jujjuya cikin sauƙi. Tare da dannawa kaɗan na linzamin kwamfuta ko taps akan madannai, za ku iya canza kowace ƙima ta decimal zuwa daidai daidai da hexadecimal!';
